dc_description_s: These data layers represent zoning for Winnebago County, Wisconsin in 2018. It is a feature class within the geodatabase NWinnebago_Zoning_2018.gdbN. The feature layers included in this geodatabase are NWinnebago_Airport_2018N, NWinnebago_General_2018N and NWinnebago_Shoreland_2018N.
dct_provenance_s: Arthur H. Robinson Map Library - University of Wisconsin
dc_subject_sm: Zoning - Maps, City Planning, County Ordinances
